layout/checkout:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>{{ head.title }}</title>
    {{{ head.meta_tags }}}
    {{{ head.config }}}
    <link href="{{ head.favicon }}" rel="shortcut icon">
    {{#block "head"}}{{/block}}
    {{{ stylesheet '/assets/css/theme.css' }}}
    {{{ checkout.checkout_head }}}
    {{{ stylesheet '/assets/css/optimized-checkout.css' }}}
    {{getFontsCollection font-display='block'}}
</head>
<body class="main{{#if theme_settings.body_width '===' 960}} nine-sixty{{/if}} {{#if theme_settings.body_width '===' 1170}} eleven-seventy {{/if}} {{#if theme_settings.body_width '===' 1280}} twelve-eighty {{/if}} {{#if theme_settings.body_width '===' 1366}} thirteen-sixty-six {{/if}} {{#if theme_settings.body_width '===' 1440}} fourteen-forty {{/if}} {{#if theme_settings.header-layout '!==' 'in-container'}} header-full-width{{/if}} {{#if theme_settings.header-layout '===' 'in-container'}} header-in-container{{/if}}">
  <svg data-src="{{cdn 'img/icon-sprite.svg'}}" class="icons-svg-sprite"></svg>

  {{#block "page"}}{{/block}} 

  

  {{{snippet 'header'}}}
        <svg data-src="{{cdn 'img/icon-sprite.svg'}}" class="icons-svg-sprite"></svg>

        {{#and settings.privacy_cookie settings.is_eu_ip_address}}
            {{> components/common/cookie}}
        {{/and}}

  <script>window.__webpack_public_path__ = "{{cdn 'assets/dist/'}}";</script>
       <script src="{{cdn 'assets/dist/theme-bundle.main.js'}}"></script>

       <script>
           // Exported in app.js
           window.stencilBootstrap("{{page_type}}", {{jsContext}}).load();
       </script>

    {{{footer.scripts}}}
    {{{snippet 'footer'}}}

</body> 
</html>
components/common/cookie: {{settings.privacy_cookie}}
